author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: One day I decided I would have a day To myself instead of going out with friends.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I haven't seen those "friends" since that day. It's been 2-3 years now.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: God my brother in law is annoying.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: My day consists of school,twitter,Instagram, tumblr, food, music and sleep.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: And I wonder why I don't have a life

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: Living on an island with very small minded people who tend to piss me off doesn't help.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: Monday I will start running and training for next year I think

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: Not sure if I should get up at 5 and go for a walk/run or wait until after school tomorrow... #help #newfittie

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I literally hate my body. That's why I have decided to change it.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I have 3 dogs: small, medium, large, all black with a little white bit on their chest. It's like I have the three evolutions of a Pokemon

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: Sometimes I think "yeah, I'm gonna ace today!" And then "Fuck you, fuck him, fuck her and fuck the world. I'm going back to bed"

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I don't bother watching the #news it just depresses me.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: It's always the cat got run over, never the cat was saved from falling out of a tree by a nice man walking home from work

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I'm kaput so I'm off to bed night night x

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: It's a shame I can't watch a possession movie without scaring myself so bad I almost have a panic attack.

text: Just got a flat on way home glad someone actually knows what they are doing

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: This changing of the hour has really fucked up my body clock. I will be waking up at 5 tomorrow. Great.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: Another day to be awkward at school. Sometimes I wonder why I want to be a hairdresser if every time I talk to someone I have a panic attack

text: Got choc Philly all over my iPhone.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: Can't wait for the day I can walk into the tattoo shop down in the city and tell them exactly what I want.

text: I will most probably fail this exam

text: I feel like I am going to fail this year. My first exam and I only passed by 1 point.

text: Peas in pesto for dinner

text: Am I alive or just breathing?

text: I hate my body, and I hate the way I think about myself

text: Ive only been up 6 minutes and I cant stop sneezing

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: My stomach keeps making weird noises and this is so embarassing in public

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: At least my makeup has decided to make me look good instead of a 5 year old who's found her mothers lipstick

text: Why am I always ill for Halloween ? Do ghosts come and make me ill on purpose?

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: Cause if they do they could stop right about now before the snotty gates are opened

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I won a win the lottery and buy myself a entire wardrobe of new clothes.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I think I have changed a lot in the last week. I have realized a lot of things and actually thought about some stuff.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I missed my parka so much this summer

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I hate my body so much

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I weighed myself and went through most of my clothes to find I am a small whale and hardly any of my clothes fit me anymore.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I even hated myself when I was like 5

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I shouldn't be left on my own for very long, I start to think about things that I really shouldn't think about for my own mental health.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: @username what?

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: My biggest decision today has been to take a bath or not.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: God I'm boring.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I have become one of those people who doesn't mind anything, doesn't have any actual interest in life and doesn't have a favorite anything.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I don't want to be like that.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: This bath shall be dedicated rose aching the net for things I might like. I need interests

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: Grease lightning, go grease lightning!

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: Why dont I live in America?

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I don't want longer hair, I need longer hair.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I didn't know ordering extensions would be so hard

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: Got my eyebrows done today! Yay!

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: Now dyeing my eyelashes

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I think I might start doing yoga. Put the old yoga stuff to use at least

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: There is a girl in my class that has tattooed her brows on, but in the color she dyes her hair and not her natural color (c)

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: So she has red eyebrows, and now wants to change her hair color to blonde.

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I am so bored of everyone in my class already. And we have only been at school for two months

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: This is going to be a long year

author: 583f1402-6edc-41a5-b0d9-f073aa8757c7
text: I have put on so much weight so quickly the scars on my leg has deformed my leg.
